highlights.text: “FAZ 360 E SENTA” by Mc Lindão, MC Menor MT, and DJ JHOW BEATS is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Brazil, up 16 spots at #84.
Nair Nany has the most spots on Viral Songs Brazil. “Melhor Amigo / O Que Seria de Mim - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #3.
“Nope your too late i already died” by wifiskeleton and i wanna be a jack-o-lantern has been on Viral Songs Brazil the longest, at 96 days straight.
“Jesus Ta Lá” by lisa_wuffwuff, awp, and MPPO is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Brazil at #1.
